Package: co2emissionsanalyzer
Type: Package
Title: CO2 Emissions Data Analyzer
Version: 1.0.0
Author: person("Hasan", "Ghadban", email = "ghadban1988@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Maintainer: Hasan Ghadban <ghadban1988@gmail.com>
Description: An interactive tool for downloading, processing, and visualizing CO2 emissions data by energy source and U.S. state. Includes functionality to produce line graphs and Excel reports based on user-defined inputs. Data provided by the U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA).
